data.description: *Accepted contract - showing for back up* A stunningly beautiful ranch on a double corner lot awaits a new owner! At just 3 years young, this house offers both peace of mind, and lovely finishes. You will love entertaining guests, or having eyes on your playful little ones, in your large living room, which is open to your kitchen and dining room. Each bedroom is on its own side of the house, which offers a unique floor plan for privacy. The primary suite feels luxurious, boasting a separate soaking tub, double sinks with granite counter tops, and separate shower. The walk in closet, with recent upgrades to best utilize the space, is sure to impress! On the cool summer mornings or evenings, spend your time on either your front or back covered patios. With close proximity to the base and new battery plant, this is one to see!
